

  Sample_writer - simple single threaded file writer and simple multi threaded file writer
  

  To compile single threaded sample :

   jcompile single_writer.b

  To run : 

   ./single_writer


  Compare with multi threaded sample


  To compile multi threaded sample :

   jcompile multi_writer.b
   BASIC . mult_w1.b
   BASIC . mult_w2.b
   BASIC . mult_w3.b
   BASIC . mult_w4.b
   CATALOG . mult_w1.b
   CATALOG . mult_w2.b
   CATALOG . mult_w3.b
   CATALOG . mult_w4.b

  To run sample :

   ./multi_writer

